title: 231: 10 Takeaways from Week 10
itunes:title: 231: 10 Takeaways from Week 10
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down their 10 biggest takeaways from this past weekend's action. Does the NFC have more Super Bowl contenders than the AFC (00:29)? Is there hope for the Browns (10:26)? Have the Falcons finally found a pass rush (27:55)? Are the Vikings good enough to make a deep playoff run (7:07)? All that and more on this edition of Move the Sticks presented by Ford F-Series.
